name: WillBot
0:
”Alexa, open Will Bot”
”Who is the best Mom in the world?”
”Who is the best Dad in the world?”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: will bot
des: This simple app is designed to be used only by members of my immediate family. The user can ask the app to identify either the best Mom, Dad, Sister, or Dog in the world. The app then states the name followed by a short description.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
